metadata.name: Alena Club Pass #47
metadata.description:
The “Alena Club Pass” will grant collectors access to exclusive private content and VIP experiences with Alena herself; including: a follow from her on Instagram, invites to meet ups & parties, private zoom livestreams for her club pass owners, a chance for a private dinner date with Alena, and much more!

Once you purchase this limited edition pass, you’ll get immediate access to a community here on Bubblehouse where you can talk with Alena directly and she’ll get to know you personally as one of her VIPs. Additionally, you’ll have viewing-access to exclusive, never-before-seen photos and videos that Alena will upload consistently, right here on Bubblehouse!

Oh and by the way, 100 USD will also be given to a random winner every week!
